<h2 style="font-size: 22px;">Montgomery County Community College</h2>
<strong>Blue Bell, PA</strong>

<div class="infolines">
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10">Offers credit for AP Exams</div>
        <div class="span2 alignRight">
                <div class="short-status-green">Yes</div>
        </div>
    </div>    
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10">Offers placement into higher-level courses for AP Exams</div>
        <div class="span2 alignRight">
                <div class="short-status-green">Yes</div>
        </div>
    </div>    
</div>


<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Applicants from secondary schools offering college-level courses, as well as those who have gained educational experience from other sources, may take the appropriate Advanced Placement Examination of the College Board. The college will accept a score of 3 or higher for credit. The course for which credit is granted must be one which is acceptable toward the degree for which the student is a candidate.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.mc3.edu/admissions/gettingStarted/placement" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

